ANGELES; AFFIRMATIVE ACTION; COUNSELING; RACIAL DISCRIMINATION; EMPLOYMENT 
DISCRIMINATION; EMPLOYEE RIGHTS; RACIAL RELATIONS -- LOS ANGELES 
</P>
