<P>
TRAFFIC ACCIDENTS -- ORANGE COUNTY; DRUNK DRIVING; POLICE ASSAULTS -- ORANGE 
COUNTY 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA011689-0078 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 6223 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
January 16, 1989, Monday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
